// creatureProfiles.json — per-creature physics profile overrides for mod extensibility.
//
// Add entries here to give custom creatures their own physics profile without
// modifying code.  SMAPI / Newtonsoft.Json supports // line comments.
//
// Each entry:
//   NameContains — case-insensitive substring of the creature's display name
//   Archetype    — (optional) built-in archetype name to map to:
//                  Generic, Slime, Bat, Worm, FlyingBug, Furry, Skeleton,
//                  Dragon, Elemental, Bird, HeavyBeast, Insect,
//                  FarmAnimalHeavy, FarmAnimalLight, PetDog, PetCat, FantasyFamiliar
//   Profile      — (optional) full profile object with any subset of fields:
//                  Archetype, Label, DecayRate, VelocityImpulseX, VelocityImpulseY,
//                  RandomNoiseX, RandomNoiseY, PeriodicPeriod, PeriodicImpulseX,
//                  PeriodicImpulseY, SinusoidalXFreq, SinusoidalXAmp,
//                  SinusoidalYFreq, SinusoidalYAmp, VelocityThresholdSq,
//                  ThresholdNoiseX, ThresholdNoiseY, HasTailChain, HasWings,
//                  HasFurChain, HasEarBones, TailSegments, FurSegments,
//                  HitBoneImpulseMult, HitTailFollowMult, HitWingFollowMult,
//                  HitFurFollowMult, HitHairFollowMult,
//                  IdleBodyAmplitude, IdleAppendageAmplitude,
//                  IdleRelaxedScale, IdleAlertScale, IdleTiredScale,
//                  IdleRelaxedEventRate, IdleAlertEventRate,
//                  StiffnessMult, DampingMult
//
// Idle state scales control how much the creature moves during each behavioural
// state: IdleRelaxedScale=1.0 (default), IdleAlertScale=0.55 (stiffer/smaller
// when combat-ready), IdleTiredScale=0.60 (slower when exhausted).
//
// Buggy Bugs mod: all creatures whose name contains "Buggy" are already mapped
// to the Insect archetype in monsterArchetypes.json.  Add specific overrides
// below if you need finer control per species.
//
// Example — skittery Swamp Beetle with extra random noise and faster idle events:
// { "NameContains": "Swamp Beetle", "Profile": {
//     "Archetype": "Insect", "Label": "Swamp Beetle",
//     "DecayRate": 0.74, "RandomNoiseX": 0.022, "RandomNoiseY": 0.014,
//     "IdleAlertEventRate": 2.0 } }

[
]
